01:39:57.124 --> 01:40:01.925
I heard a guy on television the other night,
he was talking about pigeons.

01:40:02.029 --> 01:40:04.930
He called them flying rats.

01:40:05.032 --> 01:40:06.932
I thought that was pretty good.

01:40:07.034 --> 01:40:11.198
What he had in mind, he was gonna give 'em
the flu or something to make them extinct.

01:40:11.305 --> 01:40:15.469
Now, uh, there was a guy that got shit on,
probably got shit on again.

01:40:15.576 --> 01:40:18.807
Then he got mad.
They ruined his suit or somethin'.

01:40:18.912 --> 01:40:23.872
